WEBVTT

00:00:00.500 --> 00:00:04.000
Hello, welcome to the introduction to dog agility training.

00:00:04.500 --> 00:00:09.000
Agility is an excellent exercise that improves your dog's activity and athletic ability.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:15.000
Today we'll learn about basic obstacle training methods.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:22.000
First, it's important to secure a safe and spacious area.

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:28.000
Start with simple obstacles and gradually increase the difficulty.

00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:33.000
All training should be adjusted to your dog's pace, don't push too hard.

00:00:34.000 --> 00:00:40.000
Providing ample rewards and praise after each success is key.

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:45.000
Regular short sessions are the most effective way to train consistently.

00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:50.000
Next time, we'll learn about creating various agility course layouts.